                        "description": "<p>Briefly, 5 biological repeats of ispg-2d, ctrl-d strains were cultured in LB medium supplemented with appropriate antibiotics in 37 \u00b0C incubator shaker till late-logarithmic phase (OD600 nm approx. 0.8). Bacteria pellets were collected and washed with deionized water by centrifugation at 4 \u00b0C, followed by freeze-drying.</p>",
